      <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=1174&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;mobile=yes" id="thread_subject">[分享]民族英雄――戚继光（9.18就要到了）</a> 
     </div> 
     <div class="bm_inf"> 
      <font class="xg1">看1011<span class="pipe">|</span>回2</font>
